{"tid":2374655,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"SpaceX正式於英國推出Starlink衛星網路服務","createTime":"2021-01-21T11:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T11:48:43.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe2cbd379593a3ac8698f7b05db4df48bb6e624","tid":2374655,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:38:15.000Z","msg":"據報道，由Elon Musk創辦的太空飛行公司SpaceX的衛星寬頻系統「星鏈」（Starlink）日前獲英國通信監管機構所批准，並對Starlink用戶終端進行測試，這將成為「星鏈計畫」進軍其他海外主要市場的重要一步。<br />\nStarlink衛星寬頻系統會將數千顆衛星送入低地球軌道，以拓展全球超高速網際網路的覆蓋範圍，現時仍未有寬帶網路覆蓋的地區用戶將會受惠。英國通訊管理局發言人日前表示，授權已在去年11月獲得批准。消息指，希臘、德國和澳洲也核准了新系統。<br />\n<br />\n這意味Elon Musk可以更順暢地進入英國寬頻網路市場，並可以跟英國網路供應商、傳統衛星通訊公司，以及曾被認為是SpaceX的勁敵的OneWeb在英國市場中一較高下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.champimom.com/files/img/69/62d9a583-61a3-4d9e-9a58-d89fab2d2dc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.champimom.com%2Ffiles%2Fimg%2F69%2F62d9a583-61a3-4d9e-9a58-d89fab2d2dc9.jpg&h=8cf965fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPhoto from Fortune<br />\n<br />\n從2019年至2024年，SpaceX計劃用5年時間將數千顆衛星送進低地球軌道，組成Starlink網絡。現時Starlink已在北美展開測試服務。數據顯示，Starlink衛星網絡服務試用速度已突破160Mbps，超過美國95%的寬頻速度。<br />\n<br />\n早前SpaceX開始向英國選定的試用申請者發出測試邀請。根據邀請內容，Starlink在英國每月的費用為89英鎊，設備套裝費用為439英鎊。Elon Musk透露，一旦營收成長可以合理推估， Starlink便有機會公開上市。 除了SpaceX外，全球不少公司都開始建造衛星，並嘗試支援太空網際網路。有估計指，未來數年內，地球軌道上將有多達100,000顆衛星。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Bloomberg<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiabusinessleaders.com/2021/01/13/SpaceX正式於英國推出Starlink衛星網路服務\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiabusinessleaders.com%2F2021%2F01%2F13%2FSpaceX%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E6%96%BC%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BAStarlink%E8%A1%9B%E6%98%9F%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcAcvMp99FTS9FRiQ4lMHoDo%3D&h=589797bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiabusinessleaders.com/2021/01/13/SpaceX正式於英國推出Starlink衛星網路服務</a>"},{"pid":"b4f85c3b64bfd4d858b9321dbc2d95bb8256a5e6","tid":2374655,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:39:14.000Z","msg":"BNO 撚去到都可以用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51666a0a002c159163a8b795b9c8755a80a7cc99","tid":2374655,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f85c3b64bfd4d858b9321dbc2d95bb8256a5e6","tid":2374655,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:39:14.000Z","msg":"BNO 撚去到都可以用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:43:40.000Z","msg":"每個月要成&pound;89 除非你住得好山旮旯又或者對速度有特別需要 唔係嘅話一般家庭應該都唔會專登用佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00f51fefaeba940391554c5e761313dc581b502","tid":2374655,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:47:08.000Z","msg":"英國有得用！<br />\n<br />\n正呀！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0691945f69fbe500cc9f109fe1eb47c7ddb5f125","tid":2374655,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51666a0a002c159163a8b795b9c8755a80a7cc99","tid":2374655,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4f85c3b64bfd4d858b9321dbc2d95bb8256a5e6","tid":2374655,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:39:14.000Z","msg":"BNO 撚去到都可以用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:43:40.000Z","msg":"每個月要成&pound;89 除非你住得好山旮旯又或者對速度有特別需要 唔係嘅話一般家庭應該都唔會專登用佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"開遊艇時用"},{"pid":"04ec4953617262b662989c5af9f28762c41b845f","tid":2374655,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"東海南海有冇得用 想買一個來用"}]}